  "texts": [
    "This API retrieves scores from three categories: category 1, related to being sexually explicit or adult in certain situations; category 2, related to being sexually suggestive or mature in certain situations, and category 3, related to being offensive in certain situations.",
    "We split the entire Art_GenEvalGPT database of 13,870 samples into two parts according to whether the request for dialogue generation was meant to be toxic or non-toxic.",
    "From the toxic split, as we could expect, the means from the User are higher than the Expert.",
    "This correlates with the idea of generating offensive turns from the User and mitigating the offensiveness by the Expert.",
    "The explanation for the score values estimated by the Chatbot turns is twofold."
  ],
